 of boundary conditions on these\nsub-sequential limits. Let us mention that the result should be instrumental in\nthe study of critical exponents as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 May 2015 18:57:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-03"}
